title: cmd/gc: ICE cgen_proc: unknown call NAME
body:
$ ~/go/bin/go version
go version go1.3beta2 +4b3cdcb02f2d Mon May 26 19:20:45 2014 +0400 linux/amd64

$ cat m2.go
package main

func main() {
	var a []int
	defer copy(a, a)
}

$ ~/go/bin/go run m2.go 
./m2.go:5: internal compiler error: cgen_proc: unknown call NAME

May be related to issue #8039.
